title: Did Trump's manager give 55 million dollars to Bancorp to N95 unmanageable masks?
subtitle: FEMA stated that she knew the company "don't make" masks because the company is a broker, not a factory.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The Trump administration awarded a $55 million contract to a bankrupt company without employees to provide N95 with masks that it didn't make.
